const ENVIRONMENT = 'Dev'

exports.baseUrl               =  ENVIRONMENT === 'Prod' ? 'https://imit-client.herokuapp.com' : 'http://localhost:4000'
exports.apiServer             =  ENVIRONMENT === 'Prod' ? 'https://imit-server.herokuapp.com' : 'http://localhost:9000'
exports.apiBaseUrl            =  exports.apiServer + '/api'
exports.authCookieName        = 'schoolman_token'
exports.applicationReceiver   = 'training@imitpford.org'
